59
00:05:45,100 --> 00:05:47,000
Naši pronásledovatelé se blíží, musíme se rozdělit.

60
00:05:47,100 --> 00:05:48,000
Jo!

61
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:53,000
Tudy!

62
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:56,000
Tady.

63
00:05:56,100 --> 00:05:57,000
Díky.

64
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,000
Cordelie!

65
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,000
Co zas?

66
00:06:01,250 --> 00:06:02,800
Tudy!

67
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:05,000
Počkej! Proč vždy musím běžet taky?

68
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:16,900
Stůjte!

69
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,000
Copak?

70
00:06:30,780 --> 00:06:31,660
Jsou pronásledováni.

71
